eam/apps/1081300/extras/232e854ada27159e709f35825798b249.poster.avif?t=1756143204\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081300/extras/232e854ada27159e709f35825798b249.webm?t=1756143204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081300/extras/232e854ada27159e709f35825798b249.mp4?t=1756143204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081300/extras/784b6c7059ca739f280e4b55289f92fa.avif?t=1756143204\" width=600 height=75 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rebindable controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flexibility in input, hotswap between mouse&Keyboard and controllers. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Font options for the dialogue for ease of reading.'</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We want musketeers of all shapes and sizes to enjoy Sacre Bleu. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081300/extras/84e31b150ab54265b9cc4aa9e6005df5.poster.avif?t=1756143204\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081300/extras/84e31b150ab54265b9cc4aa9e6005df5.webm?t=1756143204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081300/extras/84e31b150ab54265b9cc4aa9e6005df5.mp4?t=1756143204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081300/extras/6416752f162e037a0d81e